txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.

Wanted: Dirty wings from the bats in the northern Shire. Bounders are looking for proof of those who are assisting them in keeping the Shire safe. Deliver the items to Hal Hornblower at Hobbiton centre.
'Bats? I'm pleased that I am in the safety of Hobbiton.\n\n'Thank you, kindly.'
'You may want to try looking around Scary or Brockenborings... I hear that there are fluttering things there at night.'
Hal Hornblower wants dirty wings. Hal can be found near the stable in the centre of Hobbiton.
Deliver the dirty wings to Hal Hornblower in Hobbiton
You have accepted a task to acquire dirty wings for the Bounders of the Shire. They have deputized Hal Hornblower to collect the items near the stables in Hobbiton.
Wanted: Dirty wings from the bats in the northern Shire.
